  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. This model has been applied in clinical research settings to support pre-market submissions for posterior spinal fixation devices, informing assessments of construct stiffness and fatigue life under physiological loading. The assessment team determined that simulation credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory decision.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-compression-bending-claim-001",
